title: Trump fetes Saudi crown prince with pseudo-state dinner attended by Cristiano Ronaldo

author: Heather Hunter
description: Pope Leo XIV ignited a wave of criticism across social media this week after issuing a series of public messages calling for stronger climate action, expanded compassion toward migrants, and inclusion of transgender individuals. The controversy accelerated after the pontiff posted on X on Nov. 16, urging world leaders to prioritize justice for vulnerable communities. […]
title: Pope Leo XIV draws online backlash over climate, immigration and transgender outreach

author: Callie Patteson and Maydeen Merino
description: The House has voted in favor of rolling back environmental restrictions on drilling and mining in northern Alaska and Wyoming imposed during the Biden administration that Republicans claim have hindered fossil fuel development and energy dominance in both states.  House Republicans advanced three resolutions of congressional disapproval in a series of votes Tuesday afternoon, starting […]
title: House votes to cancel Biden drilling and mining restrictions in Alaska and Wyoming

author: Heather Hunter
description: A financial expert is urging Americans to dramatically rethink their holiday shopping lists, including cutting out gifts for adult extended family members, as families across the country brace for Christmas gift shopping. Appearing on Fox News, personal finance coach Jade Warshaw warned viewers to rein in spending and prioritize children when setting a holiday budget. […]
title: Money expert says skip gifts for adults, even grandma, to save this holiday season

author: David Sivak and Ramsey Touchberry
description: Senate Majority Leader John Thune (R-SD) is facing mounting Senate calls, including from members of his own party, to roll back a controversial provision tucked into the shutdown-ending funding bill that allows senators to sue the Justice Department for financial damages. Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley (R-IA) said Tuesday that he was inclined to […]
title: Thune fields Senate GOP backlash over ‘Arctic Frost’ surveillance provision

author: Brady Knox
description: Journalist Jamal Khashoggi’s widow criticized President Donald Trump over his comments surrounding her husband’s death. title: Khashoggi’s widow rebukes Trump for ‘justifying’ husband’s death in meeting with Saudi crown prince
